title: Large 1 Bedroom and Den with Private Balcony!
posting_body: ['Invite your friends over to our pet friendly community for a barbeque on our rooftop deck and enjoy the picturesque view of Lake Union, the Cascade Mountains, and Downtown Seattle!', 'Community Amenities', 'Fitness Center • Rooftop BBQ/Picnic Area • Available 24/7 to Assist You • On-Site Maintenance •', 'On-Site Management • Online Resident Portal •', 'Courtesy Patrol •', 'Assigned Garage Parking Available • Recreation Room • Near Public Transportation • Sundeck • Sauna', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Quartz Counter-tops with Glass Tile Back-splash • Dishwasher •', 'Stainless Steel Energy Efficient Appliances • Hardwood Inspired Floors • Microwave • Refrigerator • Additional Storage Available • Private Balcony/Patio • Washer/Dryer • Disposal', 'Stop in and find your dream home!', 'The Summit at Lake Union', '1735 Dexter Ave N', 'Seattle, WA 98109', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Url: <URL>', 'Here at The Summit at Lake Union, we offer renovated apartments complete with modern kitchens and baths.', 'Make yourself at home in our community by inviting your friends over for a barbeque on our rooftop deck and enjoying the picturesque view of Lake Union, the Cascade Mountains, and Downtown Seattle.', "The convenience of our close proximity to Downtown Seattle, I-5, Hwy 99, and public transportation means that you'll have more time to relax, put your feet up, and enjoy all the comforts of home.", 'Here at The Summit we love pets!', ' Pets - Max 2 allowed, Rent $25.00, Deposit $400.00', 'Comments:', 'A deposit and rent charge is required.', 'Restrictions:', 'Please inquire with a leasing Specialist for additional details regarding Pet Fees, Breed Restrictions and Pet Deposit.', 'Stop in today!', 'Mon-Sat:', '9AM-6PM', 'Sun:', 'CLOSED', 'Federal law prohibits housing discrimination on the basis of race, color, national origin, religion, sex, familial status, or disability.', '* Prices and availability are subject to change without notice.']
